ets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6860a67ae7395c6e62611227c405c56095c6adb4","tid":1593613,"uid":271400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:23:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70dc7f7a0164a241f7032f5e674ee379ccebf496","tid":1593613,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:24:26.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員、前教統局局長李國章表示，推行通識科理念正確，但執行方面有問題，包括受過訓練的通識科老師不足，又說社會混亂有很多理由，不只是「通識教壞學生」那麼簡單，貧富懸殊是主因。<br />\n<br />\n李國章說，不想批評老師，但希望老師反省一下是否以身作則，為香港社會為下一代着想，又說看到有老師不負責任。<br />\n<br />\n被問到如果問題出於師資，是否需要審查通識課本，李國章說「樣樣都要做」，首先要教好老師，如果老師不好，即使提供最好的教材都沒用，又說老師在堂上討論政治沒有問題，最重要是不要把自己理念灌輸予學生。<br />\n<br />\n被問到會否支持引入反蒙面法，他認為如果無法執行，立法都沒有意思。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482508-20190925.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482508-20190925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9NjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=210d6d6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1482508-20190925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=60c30d1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1482508-20190925.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6a1cb18fd78b8a4dc390c10e55d3b935a921c405","tid":1593613,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:25:00.000Z","msg":"又一個仆街"},{"pid":"27b40c66392ce476e9d404e6402f214e25462ff4","tid":1593613,"uid":62799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:27:28.000Z","msg":"搵人獅鳥左呢條仆街算吧啦"},{"pid":"1ffb1c5f724a97fe5ec77238aaaeb5c9edc1f768","tid":1593613,"uid":102529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:28:57.000Z","msg":"講來講去只係想話比人知，唔係班官嘅問題，完！<br />\n<br />\n無討論價值，請善用不推不回覆！"},{"pid":"616b419eb51e5a53951bc0a108a07d33fafc5e4a","tid":1593613,"uid":